{"type":"message-part","messageId":"5cf369f2-6537-43a6-ab1e-10968baec7b1","role":"user","index":0,"part":{"type":"text","text":"# Preserving your work\n\nSave a copy of files you create during this task to `/logs/artifacts/`. This directory is preserved after the run so outputs can be inspected. Organize with subdirectories if helpful (e.g., `/logs/artifacts/code/`, `/logs/artifacts/reports/`). The directory already exists and is writable.\n\n---\n\n# TypeScript Windmill Script with Multiple Default Parameters\n\n## Background\n\nWindmill scripts frequently accept optional configuration parameters with sensible defaults. TypeScript's default parameter syntax maps directly to Windmill's UI — parameters without a value use the default, while those with a value are treated as optional in the form. This task tests your ability to write a script with several optional parameters.\n\n## Requirements\n\n- Create a TypeScript script at `/home/user/windmill-project/f/scripts/format_price.ts`.\n- Export an async `main` function with this signature:\n  ```typescript\n  export async function main(\n    amount: number,\n    currency: string = \"USD\",\n    decimals: number = 2,\n    prefix: string = \"\"\n  )\n  ```\n- The function must return a formatted price string:\n  - Format: `` `${prefix}${amount.toFixed(decimals)} ${currency}` ``\n  - Example: `main(9.5)` → `\"9.50 USD\"`\n  - Example: `main(1234.5, \"EUR\", 0, \"~\")` → `\"~1235 EUR\"`\n- Create the metadata file `/home/user/windmill-project/f/scripts/format_price.script.yaml` with:\n  - `summary: \"Format a monetary amount as a price string\"`\n  - `language: typescript`\n\n## Implementation Guide\n\n1. Create `f/scripts/format_price.ts`:\n   ```typescript\n   export async function main(\n     amount: number,\n     currency: string = \"USD\",\n     decimals: number = 2,\n     prefix: string = \"\"\n   ) {\n     return `${prefix}${amount.toFixed(decimals)} ${currency}`;\n   }\n   ```\n2. Create `f/scripts/format_price.script.yaml` with summary and language fields.\n\n## Constraints\n\n- Project path: `/home/user/windmill-project`\n- Default values: `currency=\"USD\"`, `decimals=2`, `prefix=\"\"`\n- Use `amount.toFixed(decimals)` for formatting\n\n## Integrations\n\nNone."}}
